name: ʆυՈ૦
description:
ʆυՈ૦ is based on Jupiter. the name comes from NASA's space probe of the same name, which gave us unprecedented insights into the gas giant. the art represents the spiral storms seen on the surface of the planet, with a thin ring surrounding it.

this is part of my 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 collection. it combines my love for space & astronomy, with an abstract monochrome art style. every artwork is a satisfying infinite loop of motion.
